  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I dashed into a side entrance of one of those houses and hid behind those big doors I was talking about.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I must have been there for half an hour at least.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was surprised they couldn't hear my heart beating, because it was beating so hard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think I wet my pants, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CRYING] I feel, I feel angry every time-- [CRYING] just when I think about that, that situation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But those were some of the situations we had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, some of the other things that went on-- to get my bicycle I had to go through a, a park [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] where I weren't supposed to be there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the only way I could get there was by going through the park.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I used to go in and rent a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think I, I'd like to illustrate a point which is important.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "On one occasion, I, I thought I'd lost my money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
